  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink72-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaḷ pulavi nīkkit taṉṉōṭu putuppuṉal āṭa vēṇṭiya talaimakaṉ
          kaḷavukkālattup puṉalāṭṭu nikaḻntataṉai avaḷ kēṭpat tōḻikkuc colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink72">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>vayaṉmala rāmpaṟ kayilamai nuṭaṅkutaḻait</l>
          <l>titalai yalkuṟ ṟuyalvaruṅ kūntaṟ</l>
          <l>kuvaḷai yuṇka ṇēer melliyaṉ</l>
          <l>malarār malirniṟai vanteṉap</l>
          <l>puṉalāṭu puṇartuṇai yāyiṉa ḷemakkē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>           This girl with the soft nature, </l> 
<l rend="indent4">           beautiful kohl-lined eyes like waterlilies,</l> 
<l rend="indent4">           tresses which start to swing down to her hips [marked with] beauty spots, </l> 
<l rend="indent4">           and swaying foliage (grass skirt?) attached by a clasp </l> 
<l rend="indent4">           [in the form of] a white lotus blooming the field – </l> 
<l>         She has become a friend to me, to unite with while bathing in the flood, </l> 
<l>         because the full flood came, crammed with blossoms. </l> 
        
        

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
